Sotto Voce
Discworld ritual help
Sotto Voce

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Sotto Voce -- Creates a bond between you and another object or person.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Sotto Voce infuses an object or person with a divine presence. You need a holy
symbol to perform this ritual. This presence then informs you of its location
for a brief period of time.
.EP
